521
00:37:07,492 --> 00:37:09,703
<i>Baiklah, kalau begitu, beri tahu caranya.</i>

522
00:37:09,786 --> 00:37:13,248
<i>Tidak, giliranmu memberitahuku, Clarice.</i>

523
00:37:13,331 --> 00:37:16,709
<i>Kau tak bisa menawariku liburan
