605
00:44:23,281 --> 00:44:26,075
<i>Ini terasa sangat menyenangkan.
Katakan kepadaku, Clarice.</i>

606
00:44:26,159 --> 00:44:28,035
<i>Apa kenangan terburuk di masa kecilmu?</i>

607
00:44:28,119 --> 00:44:30,663
- Astaga, Starling!
- Bisa kubantu, Tuan Krendler?

608
00:44:30,746 --> 00:44:32,748
Apa yang kau lakukan
duduk di tempat gelap, Starling?

609
00:44:32,832 --> 00:44:34,458
Berpikir tentang kanibalisme.

610
00:44:34,542 --> 00:44:36,585
Staf Departemen Kehakiman
juga sedang berpikir.

